{% set description %}
  Preventing wrapping list elements can be achieved with the <code>nowrap</code> prop.
{% endset %}

{% set notes %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>Nowrap prop only works with inline and flex display, it has no effects on block display.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>This prop prevents list elements from wrapping. This means that list items can overflow the parent container when there's no space enough. Resize the window to see how element behave below.</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
  
{% endset %}

